text: Clubb Creek is a stream in Bollinger County in the U.S. state of Missouri. It is a tributary of Hawker Creek.Zalma, MO, 7.5 Minute Topographic Quadrangle, USGS, 1963 (1985 rev.) Clubb Creek has the name Abe Clubb, a pioneer settler. ==See also== *List of rivers of Missouri ==References== Category:Rivers of Bollinger County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Missouri
title: Clubb Creek
